metadata.name: N.F "AMITTA"
metadata.description:
>Amitta, the Technomagic Gunslinger

>[CURIOSITY]

Technomagic was created by Yuuji Takahara, one of the best cientists from NEO TEK, to simulate magic on the real life.

>[REWARDS]

>This piece gives to the first owner the right to ask me for a Physical Fineart Print of this art.

>(uwucrew holder only) The winner of the auction will receive a NEK-UWU derivative on Opensea.
